:<font size="15">מלאכה</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
מלאכה / melâ'kâh / mel-aw-kaw'

===Etymology===
From the same as {{HH|4397}}; 

===Noun===
'''מלאכה'''

# Properly deputyship, that is, ministry; generally employment (never servile) or work (abstractly or concretely); also property (as the result of labor): - business, + cattle, + industrious, occupation, (+ -pied), + officer, thing (made), use, (manner of) work ([-man], -manship).

